Subject: Obsolescence server Netwrix
Description:
Dear Support,

We are working to assess and improve the IT obsolescence management practices, particularly regarding security risks and regulatory compliance.
Socredo is using you product « Netwrix Endpoint Protector ». 
The server version is 5.9.4.1.
The client version is 6.2.4.2000. 

The application is installed on a virtual machine running Ubuntu 18.04.6 LTS.
This distribution is considered obsolete.
We would like to migrate to a more recent and supported version. 

Could you please get back to us with your technical recommendations?

Regards.
What_We_Know__c: 2025.04.17: The customer would like to migrate to a more recent and supported version.
Next_Steps__c: 2025.04.17: Shared steps to import and migrate the server to a new VM.
Solution_Comment__c: server was updated to the latest version 5.9.4.2
